body:
### Selamat Datang..

Laman ini adalah hasil auto-generate sebagai permulaan mudah untuk mencipta laman web.
Di bawah adalah panduan untuk menggunakan templat yang disediakan.   

Laman ini dibuat menggunakan mobile phone saya.
Masih dalam pembinaan dan pembelajaran.   


You can author your page content here [using GitHub Flavored Markdown](https://guides.github.com/features/mastering-markdown/), select a template crafted by a designer, and publish. After your page is generated, you can check out the new `gh-pages` branch locally. If you’re using GitHub Desktop, simply sync your repository and you’ll see the new branch.

##  Designer Templates
We’ve crafted some handsome templates for you to use. Go ahead and click 'Continue to layouts' to browse through them. You can easily go back to edit your page before publishing. After publishing your page, you can revisit the page generator and switch to another theme. 


### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Pages? Check out our [documentation](https://help.github.com/pages) or [contact support](https://github.com/contact) .

Come back for updates. Thank you.
